item.title: CVE-2023-1625|2023-09-24T00:08:12.738Z -- n%2Fa -- openstack-heat
item.description: An information leak was discovered in OpenStack heat. This issue could allow a remote, authenticated attacker to use the 'stack show' command to reveal parameters which are supposed to remain hidden. This has a low impact to the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of the system.
